{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"91841fb202","title":"毛泽东会见斯里兰卡总理班达拉奈克夫人时的谈话（节录）","origin":"外交部绝密文件，文特69","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"268d44b293","index":0,"year":1972,"month":6,"day":28,"articleId":"91841fb202"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a8d426655a","type":"title","text":"会见斯里兰卡总理班达拉奈克夫人时的谈话（节录）毛泽东（未经本人审阅）","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"91841fb202"},{"id":"c19f3e6dc6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：我们这个国家也有人家骂我们，说是整了左派。我们的“左派”是什么一些人呢？就是火烧英国代办处的那些人。今天要打倒总理，明天要打倒陈毅，后天","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"91841fb202"},{"id":"b50f1eb852","type":"appellation","text":"要打倒叶剑英。这些所谓“左”派现在都在班房里头。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"91841fb202"},{"id":"40e399123b","type":"paragraph","text":"周恩来：头子在班房里。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"91841fb202"},{"id":"151456eddb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：那些年轻人是受骗的。我们这里早几年天下大乱，你还不知道呢。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"91841fb202"},{"id":"62616a3a54","type":"paragraph","text":"班：我听说了一点。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"91841fb202"},{"id":"0d15f6b2e6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：全国各地都打，全面，内战，就是ALl-ROUND CIVIL WAR。 现在好多了。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"91841fb202"},{"id":"fb681208d8","type":"paragraph","text":"班：就是自己人之间打内战吗？","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"91841fb202"},{"id":"5158e42a02","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：两边都发枪，一共发了一百万支枪吧。这一派军队支持这一派，那一派军队支持那一派，打。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"91841fb202"},{"id":"2693c518ef","type":"paragraph","text":"周：名义上是抢枪，实际上是送枪。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"91841fb202"},{"id":"cc71e9f3eb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：他们外交部，她们（指王海容、唐闻生）这一派是“右”派，就是保守派，靠边站，弄得吃不下饭，睡不着觉。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"91841fb202"},{"id":"12102f1669","type":"paragraph","text":"班：为什么？","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"91841fb202"},{"id":"52335c5d7f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：被那些“左”派夺了权。一个半月，权不在我们手里，在那些所谓“左”派的手里。这些所谓左派，其实就是反革命。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"91841fb202"},{"id":"271dacf390","type":"paragraph","text":"没有多少问题，几个月过去了，几年过去了，总后台的人现在也过去了，叫林彪。（班夫人点头）坐一架飞机往苏联去，其目的是想见上帝。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"91841fb202"},{"id":"4798d70e9e","type":"paragraph","text":"班：见上帝？","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"91841fb202"},{"id":"7650cb89b1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：是啊，摔下来了，见上帝去了。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"91841fb202"},{"id":"2f75488d41","type":"paragraph","text":"班：噢，我明白了。（众笑）后来飞机怎么样了？我不大清楚。飞机掉下来了，","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"91841fb202"},{"id":"b96d8549b7","type":"appellation","text":"还是过到苏联去了？","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"91841fb202"},{"id":"4a52df91ae","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：我也不知道。他自己要摔。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"91841fb202"},{"id":"ef7ab95c70","type":"paragraph","text":"（外交部绝密文件，文特69）","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"91841fb202"}],"page":{"id":"407f9a7ad0","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"91841fb202","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}